cross: Dendrobium Daflo x Dendrobium Burana White
location: National Cheng Kung University Fall Orchid Show, Taiwan

measurements.description: Seventy-nine flowers on six upright inflorescences up to 52 cm; plant well-grown; sepals and petals white, intensely flashed purple, more intense centrally; lip white overlaid dark fuchsia-purple, keels fucshia-purple, white mid-area; column purple, anther cap white; substance firm; texture matte.
